    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/dff3ad4204a20217414add677d075f50.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a Paramita's officer trapped on a quest to uncover the truth behind a shadowy cult and find his missing wife. Navigate through a surreal places filled with impossible geometry, unraveling sinister secrets and confronting the manifestations of human primal fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/fc2010331b996f6f3a214e3e496d78c0.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/fc2010331b996f6f3a214e3e496d78c0.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/fc2010331b996f6f3a214e3e496d78c0.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/d9489aec87da5bb09ab0cf9a4c1d844b.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/d9489aec87da5bb09ab0cf9a4c1d844b.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/d9489aec87da5bb09ab0cf9a4c1d844b.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ESCHALISM </strong>is set in a dystopian alternate history where Indonesia never gained independence, <strong>Verenigd Oost Indische-Kyōdō Tō (V.O.K.)</strong>. In this alternate history, the Netherlands and Japan have maintained a dual colonial regime. Amidst this dystopian backdrop, a sinister cult seeks to harness humanities primordial fears, with mind older than mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/7bb906a05c63136ad0dc92b641099041.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/7bb906a05c63136ad0dc92b641099041.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/7bb906a05c63136ad0dc92b641099041.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/2624dd1aeffbfd187ed0b0cbac1c952d.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/2624dd1aeffbfd187ed0b0cbac1c952d.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/2624dd1aeffbfd187ed0b0cbac1c952d.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a richly detailed environment inspired by the &quot;House of Leaves&quot;, where spatial logic is constantly defied.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/50dbbd257c93e281ec56ccc463f9b61c.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/50dbbd257c93e281ec56ccc463f9b61c.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/50dbbd257c93e281ec56ccc463f9b61c.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/97322a9fd11531fdf93a311cb8a4190a.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/97322a9fd11531fdf93a311cb8a4190a.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/97322a9fd11531fdf93a311cb8a4190a.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience versatile combat that seamlessly shifts between isometric and first-person perspectives. Engage in strategic, resource-driven battles against the nightmarish manifestations of the cult, where every bullet counts and your wits are as crucial as your aim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/097e6fdb0e5f6dc819b6460b60cd9478.poster.avif?t=1753954852\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/097e6fdb0e5f6dc819b6460b60cd9478.webm?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147850/extras/097e6fdb0e5f6dc819b6460b60cd9478.mp4?t=1753954852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a narrative of identity, loss, and the horrific consequences of human ambition, inspired by classic cosmic horror and psychological thrillers.</p>",
